description: You see a large pool below a waterfall.
You are floating along a river.  The current here is weak but is slowly
carrying you eastward.  The south bank is choked with a thick growth
of trees, and does not seem to provide anyplace to land.  On the north
bank, you can make out a small trail leading up the side of a mountain,
but a sign reading "{RClosed For Construction{x" blocks your way.
The river flows off to the west as far as the eye can see, and to the
east the river takes a sharp turn north.
